dentifier":"s:4OUDS29AllSizeSemanticTokensProviderP","text":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","title":"sizes","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of size semantic tokens to use for link sizes"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LinkComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"links"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}]},"doc://OUDS/documentation/OUDS/AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TokensProvider","preciseIdentifier":"s:4OUDS14TokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeMultipleSemanticTokens","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic012SizeMultipleB6TokensP","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticTokens","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB6TokensP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","abstract":[{"text":"Something which provides all semantic tokens of size","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/ouds\/allsizesemantictokensprovider","type":"topic"}}}